  "texts": [
    "After displacement predictions were made, a onedimensional uniform smoothing filter was applied to the prediction to avoid errors in predictions that lead to sudden major shift from frame to frame in a registration.",
    "Supplementary Fig. 1 shows a registration example from a frame within a video.",
    "A registered video was generated for each stenosis box obtained after Algorithm 2.",
    "Algorithm 4: Segmentation algorithm.",
    "The segmentation algorithm takes an image as input and full videos can be segmented by applying the algorithm to each image contained in it."
